{"url":"https://sougouenergy.jp/","html":"\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"ja\">\n<head>\n\t<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n\t<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no\">\n\t<title>綜合エナジー株式会社 </title>\n\t<script src=\"https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.4/jquery.min.js\"></script>\n\t<link href=\"https://sougouenergy.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/sougouenergy/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\t<script src=\"https://sougouenergy.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/sougouenergy/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js\"></script>\n\t<link href=\"https://sougouenergy.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/sougouenergy/bootstrap/css/bs-button-style.min.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\n\t<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://sougouenergy.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/sougouenergy/style.css?1782155374\" media=\"all\">\n\t<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://sougouenergy.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/sougouenergy/js/index.js\"></script>\n\t<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"https://sougouenergy.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/sougouenergy/js/bxslider/jquery.bxsliderjquery.bxslider.css\">\n\t<script src=\"https://sougouenergy.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/sougouenergy/js/bxslider/jquery.bxslider.min.js\"></script>\n\t<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://sougouenergy.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/sougouenergy/js/contents.js\"></script>\n\t<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://sougouenergy.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/sougouenergy/js/tile/jquery.tile.js\"></script>\n\t<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://sougouenergy.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/sougouenergy/js/dlTableSet-master/jquery.dlTableSet.js\"></script>\n\t<script src=\"https://yubinbango.github.io/yubinbango/yubinbango.js\" charset=\"UTF-8\"></script>\n\t<link href=\"https://sougouenergy.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/sougouenergy/js/slick/slick-theme.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\t<link href=\"https://sougouenergy.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/sougouenergy/js/slick/slick.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\t<script src=\"https://sougouenergy.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/sougouenergy/js/slick/slick.min.js\"></script>\n\t<link href=\"https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.0.7/css/all.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\t<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"https://sougouenergy.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/sougouenergy/img/icon.ico\" />\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"我社は、創業以来、地域社会へのエネルギーの安定供給と安全で快適で経済的なドライブの提供に努めてまいりました。\r\n今後はより一層、安心・安全・便利そして環境に優しい仕組みと地域社会における災害時対応のインフラ施設の提供で地域の皆様に信頼され、\" />\n<meta name='robots' content='max-image-preview:large' />\n<link rel='dns-prefetch' href='//s.w.org' />\n\t<style type=\"text/css\">\r\n\t.wp-pagenavi{float:left !important; }\r\n\t</style>\r\n  <link rel='stylesheet' id='colorbox-theme3-css'  href='https://sougouenergy.jp/wp/wp-content/plugins/jquery-colorbox/themes/theme3/colorbox.css?ver=4.6.2' type='text/css' media='screen' />\n<link rel='stylesheet' id='colorbox-css-css'  href='https://sougouenergy.jp/wp/wp-content/plugins/jquery-colorbox/css/jquery-colorbox-zoom.css?ver=1.4.33' type='text/css' media='all' />\n<link rel='stylesheet' id='wp-block-library-css'  href='https://sougouenergy.jp/wp/wp-includes/css/dist/block-library/style.min.css?ver=5.8.13' type='text/css' media='all' />\n<link rel='stylesheet' id='contact-form-7-css'  href='https://sougouenergy.jp/wp/wp-content/plugins/contact-form-7/includes/css/styles.css?ver=5.1.6' type='text/css' media='all' />\n<link rel='stylesheet' id='contact-form-7-confirm-css'  href='https://sougouenergy.jp/wp/wp-content/plugins/contact-form-7-add-confirm/includes/css/styles.css?ver=5.1' type='text/css' media='all' />\n<link rel='stylesheet' id='wp-pagenavi-style-css'  href='https://sougouenergy.jp/wp/wp-content/plugins/wp-pagenavi-style/css/css3_black.css?ver=1.0' type='text/css' media='all' />\n<script type='text/javascript' src='https://sougouenergy.jp/wp/wp-includes/js/jquery/jquery.min.js?ver=3.6.0' id='jquery-core-js'></script>\n<script type='text/